                'exec_image'  => $u.'1653971858474-4f2dfa7f4dc1'.$q,
                'about_col1'  => 'The Harvest Table began as a simple brief: a family wanted a dining table large enough to seat three generations at once. What we delivered was something that will outlast all of them. Crafted entirely from reclaimed Mukwa — a dense, richly grained hardwood native to Zambia — every plank was selected for character, not uniformity.',
